Some things went wrong while creating the textual confirmation table: there is no column &quot;answers&quot;. Delete the table and re-create it using the db_update script&#058; <a href="http://bbantispam.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=69" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://bbantispam.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=69</a>.<br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
